<para id="fs-id1164562477222">The term <emphasis effect="italics">force carrier particle</emphasis> is shorthand for the scientific term <emphasis effect="italics">vector gauge boson</emphasis>. From that perspective, can the Higgs boson truly be considered a <emphasis effect="italics">force carrier particle</emphasis>?</para>
